        },
        "text_KfjH3a": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Through our partnership with Hortus Supplies International, a global supplier of horticultural products, we can assist in supplying a wide range of products to grow your plants, flowers, vegetables, and fruits—from fertilizers and propagation material to crop protection and cultivation tools. <\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Serving as a dedicated market development agency in Quebec, we seamlessly connect you with the resources you need, offering expert guidance, tailored solutions, and access to the latest innovations in greenhouse technology and crop management.<\/strong><\/p>",
